     C           K#P01     SETLLAB#PL07
     C           *IN95     DOUEQ*ON
     C           K#P01     READEAB#PL07                  95
      *
     C           *IN95     IFEQ *OFF
     C           B1SKJY    ANDEQ*BLANK
      *
